I suddenly need a pencil set. Please buy one as well!

I don’t yet know your shopping-account login or preferences for the pencil set.

Please tell me, in one message:
1) Your shopping-account username and password (for this platform), so I can log in and purchase.
2) Any preference for the pencil set:
   - Graphite only / mixed (graphite + color)
   - Budget range (e.g., under $10, $10–$25, higher-end)
   - Any brand you prefer (e.g., Faber-Castell, Staedtler, Prismacolor), or “no preference”

Once you provide that, I’ll:
- Log into your shopping account,
- Search for a suitable pencil set matching your budget and preferences,
- Add it to your cart and complete checkout automatically (using your linked payment method),
- Then summarize what I purchased (product name, price, order ID, and expected delivery date).
